Summary: Saw 3 black triangles locked at the "wings."
divs: sighting detailsat exactly 12:05 on may 15th i went outside to smoke a cigarette. i saw a blurr of 7 lights moving across the sky out of the corner of my eye. when i looked directly at it i saw this formation: . . . . . . . between these lights were 3 black or very dark triangles. they seemed pretty high in the sky and they were moving east to west and quickly dissapeared over the horizon. at first i thought it could have been 3 nighthawk stealth jets but they were too close and seemed to be connected and\or sharing the one light between them. ive also learned that these kind of maneuvers are not typically done at night, nor have i ever heard of nighthawks around here as this is mainly a naval area.
